Package com.atakmap.map.layer.raster.tilereader

Class TileReader.ReadRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.map.layer.raster.tilereader.TileReader.ReadRequest
  • Enclosing class:
    TileReader
    public static final class TileReader.ReadRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    An asynchronous read request. Defines the region or tile to be read and provides a mechanism to cancel the request asynchronously.

    • Method Detail

      • cancel

        public void cancel()
        Cancels the read request. If the request is currently be serviced, an attempt is made to abort the in-progress operation.

        This method may be invoked from any thread.
